<paragraph id="203936837F0EFFFCFF6E59E9FD27FF05" blockId="8.[151,1436,151,357]" pageId="8" pageNumber="483">
<emphasis id="12F2EA917F0EFFFCFF6E59E9FBB6FF61" bold="true" box="[199,1032,151,176]" pageId="8" pageNumber="483">Recorded damage and economic importance in the orchards of Iran:</emphasis>
Causing mild economic damage to leaves and branches of almond (
<bibRefCitation id="44174B727F0EFFFCFE5759C2FD32FF05" box="[510,652,188,213]" pageId="8" pageNumber="483" refId="ref21632" refString="Rajabi, Gh. (1991) Insects attacking Rosaceous fruit trees in Iran. Vol. 3: Homoptera. Ministry of Agriculture, Tehran, 256 pp." type="book">Rajabi 1991</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
