<emphasis id="12F2EA917F0EFFFCFF6E59A1FC18FF29" bold="true" box="[199,934,223,248]" pageId="8" pageNumber="483">Recorded damage in the orchards of other parts of the world:</emphasis>
Not recorded.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="203936837F0EFFFCFF6E587AFE8BFE91" blockId="8.[151,1436,151,357]" pageId="8" pageNumber="483">
